                    <div class="modal-body">
                        <div class="col-xs-6">
                            This program checks numbers 1 to 100 for divisibility with 3, 5 and 15.
                            Displays FIZZ for numbers divisible by 3, BUZZ for numbers divisible by 5
                            and FIZZBUZZ for numbers divisible by 15.

                            <h4>Click below button to generate numbers</h4>

                            <button type="button" id="fndFizz" class="btn btn-danger">Find fizzzz</button>
                            <hr>
